item.title: [WFLY-3326] IllegalArgumentException since upgrade to Weld 2.2.0.SP1
item.description:

comments.comment:
This is an issue with Hibernate Validator: https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HV-882

Will be fixed once HV is upgraded to 5.1.1.Final (WFLY-3319)
Confirmed: I cloned the latest WIldFly snapshot from GitHub, compiled it, upgraded HV to 5.1.1.Final, and finally the issue is gone.
I cloned the latest WIldFly snapshot for 9.0.0.Alpha1 from GitHub and compiled it: the issue is gone.
Thanks for confirmation. This issue will be closed once the 8.x branch is fixed as well (currently waiting on WFLY-3319).
